===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# Drug [[smoked]] or injested for [[euphoric]] effect, ''[[w:Cannabis (drug)|Cannabis (drug)]]''.
#:''After smoking a bowl of that fine '''marijuana''', they ate some pot brownies.''
# The [[hemp]] plant itself,The psychoactive drug cannabis, also called marijuana or hashish, is produced from parts of the cannabis plant, primarily the cured flowers and gathered trichomes of the female plant. The major active chemical compound Δ9-tetrahydrocannabinol, commonly referred to as THC, has psychoactive and medicinal effects when consumed, usually by smoking or ingestion ''[[w:Cannabis sativa|Cannabis sativa]]''. 

